<h1>Grilled Cheese Sandwich</h1>
<details>
  <summary>Ingredients</summary>
  <p>
    <ul>
      <li>Butter</li>
      <li>Bread</li>
      <li>Cheese</li>
      <li>Then use CSS to style like a pro</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.w3schools.com/css/default.asp" target="blank">w3schools.com</a> is a great resource</li>
  </p>
</details>
<details>
  <summary>Step 1</summary>
  <p>Put butter on the bread</p>
</details>
<details>
  <summary>Step 2</summary>
  <p>Put the butter side down in a hot pan</p>
</details>
<details>
  <summary>Step 3</summary>
  <p>Add cheese</p>
</details>
<details>
  <summary>Step 4</summary>
  <p>Put buttered bread on top with the butter side up</p>
</details>
<details>
  <summary>Step 5</summary>
  <p>Flip when bread is golden brown</p>
</details>
<details>
  <summary>Step 6</summary>
  <p>Serve with your choice of garnishment</p>
</details>
<p> Other recipes available:</p>
<a href="https://codepen.io/mariabultena/pen/pVmbvP" target="blank">Grilled Cheese</a>
